vote.title: A resolution authorizing (1) the adoption of the City of Dallas Vision Zero Action Plan; and (2) the coordination of initiatives and partnerships necessary to implement the actions and goals set forth in the Vision Zero Action Plan - Financing: This action has no cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information for potential future costs)
